metadata.name: Eleven
metadata.description:
Large Scale work created in graphite inks and tea on 300gsm bockingford watercolour paper.  

This piece was also released as a limited edition giclee print. (sold out) 

Created and finished 11/11/2011 at 11:11 am

became a piece of VR at 11 minutes past midnight on 7/6/22
